### CCR-026 — BS-04-05 Deck Registration (AT-05)
###
### 검증:
### - POST /decks 저장 (54장 매핑)
### - 중복 UID 거부
### - GET /decks 목록
### - PATCH /tables/{id}/active_deck
### - DeckRegistered WebSocket 이벤트

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 50.1 POST /api/v1/decks — 54장 등록
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deck_name": "WSOP-FT-2026-Deck-01",
  "cards": [
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D001", "rank": 12, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D002", "rank": 11, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D003", "rank": 10, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D004", "rank": 9,  "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D005", "rank": 8,  "suit": 0 }

  ]
}

# (52장 + Joker 2 = 54장 전체 전송. 간결화 위해 5장만 표시)
#
# 예상 응답: 201 Created
# {
#   "deck_id": "dk_01HVQK...",
#   "deck_name": "WSOP-FT-2026-Deck-01",
#   "card_count": 54,
#   "created_at": "2026-04-10T14:30:00Z"
# }

### 50.2 POST /api/v1/decks — 중복 UID (같은 deck 내)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deck_name": "duplicate-test",
  "cards": [
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D001", "rank": 12, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D001", "rank": 11, "suit": 1 }
  ]
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "DUPLICATE_UID", "uid": "04A3B2C1D001" }

### 50.3 POST /api/v1/decks — 52장 미만 (Joker 제외도 안 됨)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deck_name": "incomplete",
  "cards": [
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D001", "rank": 12, "suit": 0 }
  ]
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "INSUFFICIENT_CARDS", "expected": 52, "actual": 1 }

### 50.4 GET /api/v1/decks — 덱 목록
GET {{host}}/api/v1/decks?flight_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# { "decks": [{ "id": "dk_...", "deck_name": "...", "card_count": 54, ... }] }

### 50.5 PATCH /api/v1/tables/1/active_deck — 활성 덱 설정
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1/active_deck
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deck_id": "dk_01HVQK-wsop-ft-2026"
}

# 예상: 200 OK + DeckRegistered WS broadcast

### 50.6 WS 수신: DeckRegistered (수동)
###
### wscat -c 'ws://localhost:8000/ws/lobby?token=<jwt>&format=json'
### 위 50.5 이후 수신 메시지:
### {
###   "type": "DeckRegistered",
###   "payload": {
###     "deck_id": "dk_01HVQK-wsop-ft-2026",
###     "deck_name": "WSOP-FT-2026-Deck-01",
###     "table_id": 1,
###     "card_count": 54
###   }
### }

### 50.7 DELETE /api/v1/decks/{id} — 활성 덱 삭제 차단
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/decks/dk_01HVQK-wsop-ft-2026
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: W/"1-etag"

# 예상: 409 Conflict
# { "error": "ACTIVE_DECK_CANNOT_DELETE", "message": "..." }
